<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <%- include('layouts/header.ejs') %>
    <style>
        .coming-soon-container {
            min-height: 60vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 100px; /* navbar spacing */
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .coming-soon-container h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            font-family: barett;
        }
        .coming-soon-container p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #666;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .btn-back {
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #333;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }
        .btn-back:hover {
            background-color: #555;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .icon-construct {
            font-size: 5rem;
            color: #ff9800;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('layouts/navbar.ejs') %>

    <div class="coming-soon-container">
        <i class='bx bx-wrench icon-construct'></i>
        <h1>Fitur Belum Tersedia</h1>
        <p>Maaf, halaman atau fitur ini masih dalam tahap pengembangan. Karena Aksa Buku ini adalah purwarupa (MVP) untuk project akademik, beberapa fitur lanjutan sengaja belum dibuat.</p>
        <a href="/" class="btn-back">Kembali ke Beranda</a>
    </div>

    <%- include('layouts/footer.ejs') %>
</body>
</html>
